detaileddescription.para:
Section revision must be updated under the following conditions:
Any addition, subtraction, or size change to a meta parameter section (meta ruins everything)
Removing one or more parameters from a section
Changing the size of an existing parameter in a section
Re-ordering parameters within a section
Adding a parameter anywhere other than to the end of a section
In the future this should/will be managed and generated automatically by PM, preferably with memory storage managed by an OS file system running on a SoC.
